+//   * iOS links a self-contained static archive: `merge_ios_cpp_deps`
+//     folds simdutf/highway/utfcpp into `libghostty-vt-ios.a`.
+//   * Re-exports `cargo:libdir` / `cargo:lib_filename` so prmpt's own
+//     build.rs can stage the dylib into the macOS `.app`'s
+//     `Contents/Frameworks/` (dyld can't find @rpath once the binary
